:"2017-11-22T21:33:23.000Z","msg":"之前睇過真人電影有"},{"pid":"c886248fad490fe617411f01b27f8d1e9071c14f","tid":477200,"uid":340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T21:34:21.000Z","msg":"英語對白就得中文字幕<br />\n唔係英文既就中英對照"},{"pid":"25aba683d3b5a388edcbaa33bb215fc25df2e3b4","tid":477200,"uid":54368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T21:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港咩戲都有中英字幕</blockquote><br />\n好似唔係架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯撚定唔係<br />\n最近睇個套雷神已經唔係"},{"pid":"5089afdc0136633bc1dace65289d592aeaaeb934","tid":477200,"uid":139139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T21:37:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港咩戲都有中英字幕</blockquote><br />\n好似唔係架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯撚定唔係<br />\n最近睇個套雷神已經唔係</blockquote><br />\n我都睇咗，但係唔記得咗有冇英文字。<br />\n因為多數都係聽佢講，聽唔明先望吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935d9abb17f94cd00744fe4b3d5d41944b3a12b4","tid":477200,"uid":54368,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T21:43:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港咩戲都有中英字幕</blockquote><br />\n好似唔係架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯撚定唔係<br />\n最近睇個套雷神已經唔係</blockquote><br />\n我都睇咗，但係唔記得咗有冇英文字。<br />\n因為多數都係聽佢講，聽唔明先望吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n懶係野咁<br />\n即使識英文都唔會想生食套戲<br />\n有字幕始終好睇好多, 因為非母語有D唔慣<br />\n就算係粵語戲..字幕都緊要<br />\n日文都係<br />\n我日文都叫可以生食套戲<br />\n但我唔會想生食套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d683441011a8b46caa5ea96724c721e4a8a1fc","tid":477200,"uid":139139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T21:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港咩戲都有中英字幕</blockquote><br />\n好似唔係架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯撚定唔係<br />\n最近睇個套雷神已經唔係</blockquote><br />\n我都睇咗，但係唔記得咗有冇英文字。<br />\n因為多數都係聽佢講，聽唔明先望吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n懶係野咁<br />\n即使識英文都唔會想生食套戲<br />\n有字幕始終好睇好多, 因為非母語有D唔慣<br />\n就算係粵語戲..字幕都緊要<br />\n日文都係<br />\n我日文都叫可以生食套戲<br />\n但我唔會想生食套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搭親飛機都生食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英文電影其實都好易睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd84d23a37499a77f5a3cb5b2697334c927b7cc","tid":477200,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T21:56:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港咩戲都有中英字幕</blockquote><br />\n好似唔係架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯撚定唔係<br />\n最近睇個套雷神已經唔係</blockquote><br />\n我都睇咗，但係唔記得咗有冇英文字。<br />\n因為多數都係聽佢講，聽唔明先望吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n懶係野咁<br />\n即使識英文都唔會想生食套戲<br />\n有字幕始終好睇好多, 因為非母語有D唔慣<br />\n就算係粵語戲..字幕都緊要<br />\n日文都係<br />\n我日文都叫可以生食套戲<br />\n但我唔會想生食套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搭親飛機都生食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英文電影其實都好易睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日文次次睇都係聽完好似明但又唔知係咪真係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f203668a1b9339ecb722a2276d8cb04701904c98","tid":477200,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T02:14:25.000Z","msg":"香港仲有上明天我要和昨天的妳約會咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"